thread.title: BRIEF-SODIC To Develop Residential Tourism Project in Partnership

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-SODIC To Develop Residential Tourism Project in Partnership
text:
March 11 (Reuters) - SIXTH OF OCTOBER DEVELOPMENT AND INVESTMENT CO:
* SIGNS TWO PARTNERSHIP DEALS TO DEVELOP RESIDENTIAL TOURISM PROJECT ON ABOUT 308 FEDAN PLOTS
* OWNERS OF PLOTS TO HAVE PARTICIPATION OF 28 PERCENT AND CO 72 PERCENT OF TOTAL REVENUE OF RESIDENTIAL AND COMMERCIAL UNITS
* EXPECTS TOTAL CUSTOMER CONTRACTS OF PROJECT TO REACH ABOUT EGP 15.2 BILLION DURING 7 YEARS Source: ( bit.ly/2tz1Obh ) Further company coverage:
